<lb n="0726a08" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title><note n="0726002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【縮】</note><note n="0726002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說【大】＊，〔－〕【縮】＊</note><app n="0726002"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0726003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">木槵子＝木槵【三】【縮】＊，木患【宮】＊</note><note n="0726003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">木槵子【大】＊，木槵【宋】【元】【明】【縮】＊，木患【宮】＊</note><app n="0726003"><lem wit="【大】">木槵<note n="0726004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔子〕－【和】【縮】</note><note n="0726004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子【大】，〔－〕【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726004"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【縮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【縮】">木槵</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">木患</rdg></app>經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0726a09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0726a10" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0726005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（失譯…晉錄））八字＝（（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯））【和】【縮】</note><note n="0726005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（失譯…晉錄）八字【大】，大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726005" cb:word-count="8"><lem wit="【大】">失譯<note n="0726006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【宋】【元】，人＋（名）【明】</note><note n="0726006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】，人名【明】</note><app n="0726006"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">人名</rdg></app>今附東晉錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【縮】">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0726a11" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT17p0726a1101"><note n="0726007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聞如是＝聞如是我聞【和】，如是我聞【縮】</note><note n="0726007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聞如是【大】，聞如是我聞【和】，如是我聞【縮】</note><app n="0726007"><lem wit="【大】">聞如是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">聞如是我聞</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">如是我聞</rdg></app>：</p><p xml:id="pT17p0726a1104" rend="inline">一時佛遊羅閱祇<note n="0726008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">闍耆＝闍【和】，嗜闍【縮】</note><note n="0726008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耆闍【大】，闍【和】，嗜闍【縮】</note><app n="0726008"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">耆闍<note type="cf1">K20n0862_p1226a03</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">闍耆</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">闍</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">嗜闍</rdg></app>崛山中，與
<lb n="0726a12" ed="T"/>大比丘眾一千二百五十人俱，菩薩無數，名
<lb n="0726a13" ed="T"/>稱遠聞，<note n="0726009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天人＝人天【縮】</note><note n="0726009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天人【大】，人天【縮】</note><app n="0726009"><lem wit="【大】">天、人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">人天</rdg></app>所敬。時難國王，名<note n="0726010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波流離＝波瑠璃【三】【宮】，波琉璃【和】，波瑠璃遣【縮】</note><note n="0726010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波流離【大】，波瑠璃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，波琉璃【和】，波瑠璃遣【縮】</note><app n="0726010"><lem wit="【大】">波流離</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">波瑠璃</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">波琉璃</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">波瑠璃遣</rdg></app>，遣
<lb n="0726a14" ed="T"/>使來到佛所，頂禮佛足，白佛言：「世尊！我國
<lb n="0726a15" ed="T"/>邊<note n="0726011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">小＝少【縮】</note><note n="0726011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">小【大】，少【縮】</note><app n="0726011"><lem wit="【大】">小</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">少</rdg></app>，頻<note n="0726012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歲＝年【縮】</note><note n="0726012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歲【大】，年【縮】</note><app n="0726012"><lem wit="【大】">歲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">年</rdg></app>寇賊，五穀<note n="0726013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勇＝踴【縮】</note><note n="0726013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勇【大】，踴【縮】</note><app n="0726013"><lem wit="【大】">勇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">踴</rdg></app>貴，<note n="0726014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疾病＝疫疾【三】【宮】，疾疫【和】【縮】</note><note n="0726014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">疾病【大】，疫疾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，疾疫【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726014"><lem wit="【大】">疾病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">疫疾</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【縮】">疾疫</rdg></app>流行，人
<lb n="0726a16" ed="T"/>民困苦，我恒不得安臥。如來法藏，多悉深廣；
<lb n="0726a17" ed="T"/>我有<note n="0726015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">憂務＝憂勞【宮】</note><note n="0726015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">憂務【大】，憂勞【宮】</note><app n="0726015"><lem wit="【大】">憂務</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">憂勞</rdg></app>，不得修行。唯願世尊特垂<note n="0726016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慈愍＝矜愍【三】【宮】【和】，㥤愍【縮】</note><note n="0726016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慈愍【大】，矜愍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【和】，㥤愍【縮】</note><app n="0726016"><lem wit="【大】">慈愍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【和】">矜愍</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">㥤愍</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0726a18" ed="T"/>賜我<note n="0726017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">要法＝法要【縮】</note><note n="0726017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">要法【大】，法要【縮】</note><app n="0726017"><lem wit="【大】">要法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">法要</rdg></app>！使我日夜易得修行，未來世中
<lb n="0726a19" ed="T"/>遠離眾苦。」</p>
<lb n="0726a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0726a2001">佛告王言：「若欲滅煩惱障、報障者，當貫<note n="0726018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">木槵＝木患【宮】下同</note><note n="0726018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">木槵【大】下同，木患【宮】下同</note><app n="0726018"><lem wit="【大】">木槵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">木患</rdg></app>
<lb n="0726a21" ed="T"/>子一<note n="0726019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">百＋（一）【三】【宮】【和】【縮】</note><note n="0726019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">百【大】，百一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726019"><lem wit="【大】">百</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【和】【縮】">百一</rdg></app>八，以常自隨。若行、若坐、若臥，恒<note n="0726020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝常【縮】</note><note n="0726020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，常【縮】</note><app n="0726020"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">常</rdg></app>
<lb n="0726a22" ed="T"/>至心，無分散意，稱佛陀、<note n="0726021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">達摩＝達磨【三】【宮】【縮】</note><note n="0726021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">達摩【大】，達磨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【縮】</note><app n="0726021"><lem wit="【大】">達摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【縮】">達磨</rdg></app>、僧伽名，乃過一
<lb n="0726a23" ed="T"/>木槵子，如是漸次度木槵子，若十、若二十、若
<lb n="0726a24" ed="T"/>百、若千，乃至百千萬。若能滿二十萬遍，身心
<lb n="0726a25" ed="T"/>不亂，<note n="0726022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無〕－【和】</note><note n="0726022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，〔－〕【和】</note><app n="0726022"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>諸諂曲<note n="0726023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【縮】</note><note n="0726023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，〔－〕【縮】</note><app n="0726023"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，捨<note n="0726024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝身【縮】</note><note n="0726024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命【大】，身【縮】</note><app n="0726024"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">身</rdg></app>得生第三焰天，
<lb n="0726a26" ed="T"/>衣食自然，常安樂行。若復能滿一百萬遍者，
<lb n="0726a27" ed="T"/>當得斷除百八結業，始名背生死流，趣向泥
<lb n="0726a28" ed="T"/>洹，永斷煩惱根，獲無上果。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0726a2811" rend="inline"><note n="0726025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">信＝使【明】</note><note n="0726025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">信【大】，使【明】</note><app n="0726025"><lem wit="【大】">信</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">使</rdg></app>還啟王，王大
<lb n="0726a29" ed="T"/>歡喜，遙向世尊，頭面禮佛<note n="0726026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">云＝稱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0726026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">云【大】，稱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0726026"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">稱</rdg></app>：「大<note n="0726027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＋（哉）【縮】</note><note n="0726027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善【大】，善哉【縮】</note><app n="0726027"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">善哉</rdg></app>！我當奉
<pb n="0726b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0786.0726b"/>
<lb n="0726b01" ed="T"/>行。」即勅吏民，營<note n="0726028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辦＝辨【和】【縮】</note><note n="0726028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辦【大】，辨【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726028"><lem wit="【大】">辦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【縮】">辨</rdg></app>木槵子，以為<note n="0726029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">千＝一【宋】【元】</note><note n="0726029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">千【大】，一【宋】【元】</note><app n="0726029"><lem wit="【大】">千</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">一</rdg></app>具，六親
<lb n="0726b02" ed="T"/>國戚，皆與一具。王常誦念，雖<note n="0726030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親＝視【縮】</note><note n="0726030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">親【大】，視【縮】</note><app n="0726030"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">視</rdg></app>軍旅，亦不
<lb n="0726b03" ed="T"/><note n="0726031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">廢＝癈【縮】</note><note n="0726031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">廢【大】，癈【縮】</note><app n="0726031"><lem wit="【大】">廢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">癈</rdg></app>置。又作是念：「世尊大慈，普應一切。若我
<lb n="0726b04" ed="T"/>此<note n="0726032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＋（根）【縮】</note><note n="0726032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善【大】，善根【縮】</note><app n="0726032"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">善根</rdg></app>，得免長<note n="0726033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淪＝沈【縮】</note><note n="0726033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淪【大】，沈【縮】</note><app n="0726033"><lem wit="【大】">淪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">沈</rdg></app>苦海，如來<note n="0726034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＋（身）【和】</note><note n="0726034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，當身【和】</note><app n="0726034"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">當身</rdg></app>現<note n="0726035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔我〕－【三】【宮】【縮】，〔我身〕－【和】</note><note n="0726035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我身【大】，〔－〕【和】，身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【縮】</note><app n="0726035"><lem wit="【大】">我身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【縮】">身</rdg></app>，為
<lb n="0726b05" ed="T"/><note n="0726036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（我）＋我【和】</note><note n="0726036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我【大】，我我【和】</note><app n="0726036"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">我我</rdg></app>說法。」願樂迫心，<note n="0726037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三日不食＝不食三日【縮】</note><note n="0726037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三日不食【大】，不食三日【縮】</note><app n="0726037"><lem wit="【大】">三日不食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">不食三日</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0726b0512" rend="inline">佛即應形，與
<lb n="0726b06" ed="T"/>諸眷屬，<note n="0726038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">來＋（至）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0726038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來【大】，來至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0726038"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">來至</rdg></app>其宮內，而告王曰：「莎<note n="0726039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斗＝升【和】，舛【縮】</note><note n="0726039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斗【大】，升【和】，舛【縮】</note><app n="0726039"><lem wit="【大】">斗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">升</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">舛</rdg></app>比丘，誦
<lb n="0726b07" ed="T"/>三寶名，經歷十歲，得成斯陀含果；漸次習行，
<lb n="0726b08" ed="T"/>今在普香世界，作辟支佛。」王聞是已，倍復修
<lb n="0726b09" ed="T"/>行。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0726b0902" rend="inline">佛告阿難：「何況能誦三寶名，經歷<note n="0726040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">萬數＝萬歲【和】【縮】</note><note n="0726040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">萬數【大】，萬歲【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726040"><lem wit="【大】">萬數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【縮】">萬歲</rdg></app>；
<lb n="0726b10" ed="T"/>但能聞此人名，生一念隨喜者，未來生處，常
<lb n="0726b11" ed="T"/>聞十善。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0726b1104" rend="inline">說是<note n="0726041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＝語【三】【宮】</note><note n="0726041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，語【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0726041"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">語</rdg></app>時，大眾歡喜，皆願奉行！</p></cb:div>
